  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 42\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd0\u0dbd\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The maid who stole 42 lakhs from a house is in the net",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Bambalapitiya police say that the maid was arrested for stealing 46 lakh rupees from a house in Bambalapitiya.",
        "Police found the suspect hiding this money in a washing machine at home.",
        "The police say that the suspect has stolen this amount from the money she had taken from the bank to buy a vehicle.",
        "Police say that the arrested suspect is a 40-year-old mother of three from Watawala area."
      ],
